{
  "/api/v2/admin/farms/": {
    "post": {
      "summary": "Create a new farm",
      "tags": ["Admin/Farms"],
      "description": "Creates a new farm with the provided details and associates specified users with it.\n\n## Form Fields and Validation Rules\n\n### Required Fields\nAll fields listed below are required for successful farm creation.\n\n### Field Specifications\n\n- **name**\n  - **Type**: String\n  - **Length**: 3-100 characters\n  - **Validation**: Must not be empty\n  - **Purpose**: Unique identifier for the farm\n\n- **address**\n  - **Type**: String\n  - **Length**: 5-200 characters\n  - **Validation**: Must not be empty\n  - **Purpose**: Physical location of the farm\n\n- **latitude**\n  - **Type**: String (numeric value)\n  - **Range**: Must be between -90 and 90\n  - **Validation**: Must be a valid geographic coordinate\n  - **Format**: Decimal degrees (e.g., \"12.345678\")\n\n- **longitude**\n  - **Type**: String (numeric value)\n  - **Range**: Must be between -180 and 180\n  - **Validation**: Must be a valid geographic coordinate\n  - **Format**: Decimal degrees (e.g., \"-12.345678\")\n\n- **users**\n  - **Type**: Array of integers\n  - **Validation**:\n    - Must contain at least one user ID\n    - Each ID must represent an existing user in the system\n    - Each user must have the OWNER role\n  - **Behavior**: Duplicate IDs in the request will be processed only once\n  - **Purpose**: Associates farm owners with the farm",
      "security": [
        {
          "apiKey": []
        }
      ],
      "requestBody": {
        "required": true,
        "content": {
          "application/json": {
            "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": ["name", "address", "latitude", "longitude", "users"],
              "properties": {
                "name": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Name of the farm. Required. Must be a string between 3 and 100 characters.",
                  "example": "Mi granjita"
                },
                "address": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Physical address of the farm. Required. Must be a string between 5 and 200 characters.",
                  "example": "Dirección de la granja"
                },
                "latitude": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Latitude coordinate of the farm location. Required. Must be a valid number between -90 and 90.",
                  "example": "12.345678"
                },
                "longitude": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "description": "Longitude coordinate of the farm location. Required. Must be a valid number between -180 and 180.",
                  "example": "-12.345678"
                },
                "users": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "description": "Array of user IDs to be associated with the farm. Required. Must contain at least one user ID. Each user ID must be a valid number, must exist in the system, and must have the OWNER role. Duplicate IDs are allowed in the request but will be processed only once.",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  },
                  "example": [2, 3]
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "responses": {
        "200": {
          "description": "Farm created successfully",
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "message": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "example": "Farm created successfully"
                  },
                  "data": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
